Class DocumentViewer

  • java.lang.Object
    • Steganography.Modals.DocumentViewer

  • public class DocumentViewer
extends java.lang.Object
    This DocumentViewer class is used to display a document after extracting it from a stego image in a JavaFX application modal window.
